wikipedia_page.main: Sir Douglas Maurice Warburton Elphinstone, 5th Baronet TD FFA FRSE (13 April 1909 - 5 December 1995) was a Scottish baronet. He was usually addressed simply as Douglas Elphinstone.

response: In 1908, in Durham, Christiana Georgiana Almond married the Rev. Canon Maurice Elphinstone (1874–1969), vicar of Sowerby Bridge, a younger son of Sir Howard Warburton Elphinstone, 3rd Baronet. Their eldest son, born in 1909, became Sir Douglas Elphinstone, 5th Baronet FRSE.
